385
00:42:52,195 --> 00:42:53,989
The real Daisuke?

386
00:42:54,114 --> 00:42:58,493
He didn't recognize a photo
of the fake Daisuke though.

387
00:42:59,119 --> 00:43:04,874
So, in Osaka,
