Daisuke's still alive?

393
00:43:24,394 --> 00:43:29,983
I mean, well, surely
the other guy killed him?

394
00:43:31,818 --> 00:43:35,071
If the wife is on the level,
she's a victim,

395
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:42,829
