00:53:51,020 --> 00:53:54,774
However, he wasn't the real
Daisuke Taniguchi.

501
00:53:55,900 --> 00:54:00,613
Mr. Omiura, you brokered
identity document switches, correct?

502
00:54:01,572 --> 00:54:03,950
