503
00:54:04,784 --> 00:54:08,829
The second son of the
Ikaho Onsen innkeeper?

504
00:54:09,872 --> 00:54:12,667
Yes! That's right.
You knew him?

505
00:54:13,626 --> 00:54:16,003
I think we're done here today.

506
00:54:16,212 --> 00:54:19,507
I want to know who he switched with.

507
00:54:20,591 --> 00:54:24,178
It wasn't a switch,
it was identity laundering.

508
00:54:24,804 --> 00:54:31,811
Just like dirty money, plenty of folks
want to wash their pasts clean.

509
00:54:33,938 --> 00:54:39,610
Mister lawyer, I bet you hated
